# ğŸ”¹ Node Management

```bash
kubectl get nodes
```

```bash
kubectl describe node <node-name>
```

```bash
kubectl cordon <node-name>
```
Mark node unschedulable.

```bash
kubectl drain <node-name> --ignore-daemonsets
```
Safely evict workloads.

```bash
kubectl uncordon <node-name>
```
Make node schedulable again.

