# ğŸ”¹ Troubleshooting Commands

```bash
kubectl get events
```

Sort by time:

```bash
kubectl get events --sort-by=.metadata.creationTimestamp
```

Check resource usage (Metrics Server required):

```bash
kubectl top nodes
kubectl top pods
```

